                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000115-81-defend683 t18000115-81-punish482"></join>
               fined 1s
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. Justice LAWRENCE.</p>
